Template: mok/generate
Type: password
Description: Going to generate the Machine Owner Key (MOK). Please enter passphrase?
 The passphrase you enter for this key will be required every time you want to sign a module.

Template: mok/import
Type: note
Description: Now I will import the generated key into the secure keystore in UEFI.
 The passphrase you will enter is only required once, during the following reboot.
 Please press Return to go on...

Template: mok/reboot
Type: select
Choices: yes, no
Description: Reboot your computer now to complete the enrollment of your new MOK.
 Please reboot your computer now to complete the enrollment of your new MOK.
 This is going to look somewhat similar to https://sourceware.org/systemtap/wiki/SecureBoot
